<section class="pe-section" id="investors">
  <div class="reveal">
    <div class="section-label">For Investors Who Know Healthcare</div>
    <h2>
      The firms that succeed in healthcare won't just write better checks.
      They'll eliminate the 18 months between funding and first patient.
    </h2>
    <p class="pe-subtitle">
      Your portfolio's biggest risk isn't the care model — you already picked the
      right company. It's the infrastructure gauntlet that burns runway before a
      single patient is seen. PatientOS eliminates it. AI agents automate the
      manual MCO operations. Compliant infrastructure deploys on day one. Your
      companies launch with the operational maturity their competitors won't have
      for years. That's portfolio alpha.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="pe-grid reveal">
    <div class="pe-card">
      <div class="pe-stat">10×</div>
      <div class="pe-label">Faster to first patient revenue</div>
    </div>
    <div class="pe-card">
      <div class="pe-stat">90%</div>
      <div class="pe-label">
        Of MCO operational labor automated by AI — from day one, not after a
        2-year AI transformation project
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="pe-card">
      <div class="pe-stat">$0</div>
      <div class="pe-label">Spent building compliance infrastructure</div>
    </div>
    <div class="pe-card">
      <div class="pe-stat">Day 1</div>
      <div class="pe-label">Enterprise-grade operations, deployed</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .pe-section {
    padding: 8rem 4rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .pe-section h2 {
    font-family: "DM Serif Display", serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .pe-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    max-width: 600px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .pe-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .pe-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy), var(--slate));
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.4s;
  }

  .pe-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(62, 232, 181, 0.2);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .pe-stat {
    font-family: "DM Serif Display", serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .pe-label {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .pe-section {
      padding: 5rem 2rem;
    }
    .pe-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .pe-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
